k10091218-8a4aa.jpg"></o:p></SPAN></DIV>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">Vũ Thu Hà (24/4/1992 – ĐH Lao động&amp; Xã hội)</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><o:p><BR><BR><IMG alt="Trần Thanh Tùng (2/1/1992 - ĐH Hà Nội)" src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/y0V2Vnsx49nhQPv7HdH/Image/2012/10/fclook10091211-8a4aa.jpg"></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=center><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; FONT-SIZE: 10pt">Trần Thanh Tùng (2/1/1992 - ĐH Hà Nội)<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=right><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal align=right><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Vũ Phong<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><input type="hidden" value="/c135s135/nhipsongtre/trang-1.htm" id="hidNextUsing"/></div>\r\n \r\n <div itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/webpage" style="display: none !important;">\r\n <span itemprop="name">Lộ diện ứng cử viên sáng giá cho ngôi vị Facelook 2012</span>\r\n <img id="ctl00_IDContent_ctl00_imgAvatar_2" itemprop="image" src="http://dantri21.vcmedia.vn/zoom/70_70/y0V2Vnsx49nhQPv7HdH/Image/2012/10/fclook1009121-8a4aa.jpg" alt="Lộ diện ứng cử viên sáng giá cho ngôi vị Facelook 2012" style="border-width:0px;" />\r\n <div id="static_rating" itemprop="aggregateRating" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/AggregateRating">\r\n  <span itemprop="ratingValue">9</span>\r\n  <span itemprop="bestRating">10</span>\r\n  <span itemprop="ratingCount">148</span>\r\n </div>\r\n </div>\r\n <div class="hrecipe" style="position: fixed; bottom: -1000px; left: -1000px;">\r\n <span class="item">\r\n  <span class="item">\r\n  <span class="fn">\r\n   Lộ diện ứng cử viên sáng giá cho ngôi vị Facelook 2012</span>\r\n  <