>Cùng đón Noel</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; FONT-SIZE: 13px"><IMG src="http://dantri4.vcmedia.vn/a3HWDOlTcvMNT73KRccc/Image/2012/09/31-3d70c.jpg" alt="Ăn đi con!"><BR><BR></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Tahoma; FONT-SIZE: 13px">Ăn đi con!</SPAN></P>\r\n<DIV style="TEXT-ALIGN: right" align=right><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Hồ Bích Ngọc</SPAN></DIV>\r\n<DIV style="TEXT-ALIGN: right" align=right><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold"></SPAN>Theo <SPAN style="FONT-STYLE: italic">DM</SPAN></DIV><input type="hidden" value="/c130s130/tinhyeu-gioitinh/trang-1.htm" id="hidNextUsing"/></div>\r\n \r\n <div itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/webpage" style="display: none !important;">\r\n <span itemprop="name">Album “Bố và con gái khi mẹ vắng nhà” </span>\r\n <img id="ctl00_IDContent_ctl00_imgAvatar_2" itemprop="image" src="http://dantri21.vcmedia.vn/zoom/70_70/a3HWDOlTcvMNT73KRccc/Image/2012/09/1-781a5.jpg" alt="Album “Bố và con gái khi mẹ vắng nhà” " style="border-width:0px;" />\r\n <div id="static', '', '2012-10-01 08:26:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'private', 0, 0, 0);
