 style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"">: Bùi Diễm Ngà (ĐH Ngoại thương)<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman""><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"">Gương mặt khả ái</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"">: Trần Minh Trang (ĐH KHXH&amp;NV)<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman""><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"">Gương mặt cá tính</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"">: Vũ Thu Hà (ĐH Lao động &amp; XH)<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman""><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"">Gương mặt triển vọng</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"">: Nguyễn Thanh Phong (Art Design International School)<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman""><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"">Tiết mục độc đáo nhất đêm CK</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"">: Hát ca trù "Hồng hồng tuyết tuyết" của Nguyễn Thùy Chi (HV Âm nhạc QG)<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman""><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"">Giải tài năng</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"">: Nguyễn Kim Oanh (ĐH Sân khấu Điện ảnh HN) <o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman""><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-STYLE: italic; FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-fareast-font-family: "Times New Roman"">Giải “Tự tin tỏa sáng”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: "Tahoma","sans-serif"; COLOR: black